---
/** Vista previa de métricas: tendencia 2025 (ejemplo) + bloques estilo /app (stack y actividad). */
---

<section
  data-landing-reveal
  style="--lr-delay: 96ms"
  class="rounded-3xl border border-violet-200/50 dark:border-violet-900/40 bg-white/55 dark:bg-gray-950/45 shadow-sm overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    class="px-6 py-5 border-b border-gray-200/70 dark:border-gray-800/70 bg-linear-to-r from-violet-50/60 via-white/55 to-transparent dark:from-violet-950/35 dark:via-gray-950/50 dark:to-transparent backdrop-blur"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-3">
      <div class="space-y-1 max-w-2xl">
        <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-300 uppercase" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewKicker">
          Métricas
        </p>
        <h2 class="m-0 text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewTitle">
          Gráficos que cuentan tu progreso
        </h2>
        <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewBody">
          En /app verás datos reales. Aquí hay un ejemplo ficticio de 2025 y tarjetas parecidas al dashboard.
        </p>
      </div>
      <span
        class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-amber-200/90 dark:border-amber-800/60 bg-amber-50/90 dark:bg-amber-950/40 px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-200"
        data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewBadge"
      >
        Ejemplo
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="p-6 space-y-5">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-950/50 p-3">
      <div class="h-[260px] w-full" data-landing-insights-chart aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-950/50 p-4 shadow-sm">
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStackKicker">Stack</p>
          <h3 class="m-0 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStackTitle">
            Tecnologías más usadas
          </h3>
          <p class="m-0 text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStackHint">
            Ejemplo ficticio; en /app se calcula con tus proyectos.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-4" data-landing-charts-stack-demo>
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 text-sm">
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
                <span data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStack1Name">TypeScript</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStack1Kind"> · Lenguaje</span>
              </span>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-violet-700 dark:text-violet-300">88%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-200/90 dark:bg-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="h-full w-[88%] rounded-full bg-violet-600 dark:bg-violet-500"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 text-sm">
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
                <span data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStack2Name">Astro</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStack2Kind"> · Framework</span>
              </span>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-violet-700 dark:text-violet-300">76%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-200/90 dark:bg-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="h-full w-[76%] rounded-full bg-violet-600 dark:bg-violet-500"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 text-sm">
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
                <span data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStack3Name">PostgreSQL</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStack3Kind"> · Tecnología</span>
              </span>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-violet-700 dark:text-violet-300">62%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-200/90 dark:bg-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="h-full w-[62%] rounded-full bg-violet-600 dark:bg-violet-500"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 text-sm">
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
                <span data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStack4Name">Docker</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStack4Kind"> · DevOps</span>
              </span>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-violet-700 dark:text-violet-300">41%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-200/90 dark:bg-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="h-full w-[41%] rounded-full bg-violet-600 dark:bg-violet-500"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 text-sm">
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
                <span data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStack5Name">Terraform</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewStack5Kind"> · Infra</span>
              </span>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-violet-700 dark:text-violet-300">24%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-200/90 dark:bg-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="h-full w-[24%] rounded-full bg-violet-600 dark:bg-violet-500"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-950/50 p-4 shadow-sm">
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase" data-i18n="dashboard.recent.sectionKicker">
            Actividad
          </p>
          <h3 class="m-0 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="dashboard.recent.sectionTitle">
            Actividad reciente
          </h3>
          <p class="m-0 text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActivityIntro">
            Ejemplo estático; con sesión la lista se sincroniza como en /app.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-indigo-200/60 dark:border-indigo-900/40 bg-indigo-50/40 dark:bg-indigo-950/20 p-3">
            <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="dashboard.recent.projectsTitle">Proyectos recientes</p>
            <ul class="m-0 mt-2 list-none space-y-2 p-0 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 min-w-0" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActP1">Atlas de rutas API</span>
                <span class="shrink-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActP1When">Hace 1 d</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 min-w-0" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActP2">Panel de métricas retail</span>
                <span class="shrink-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActP2When">Hace 3 d</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 min-w-0" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActP3">ETL documentación</span>
                <span class="shrink-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActP3When">Hace 5 d</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 min-w-0" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActP4">SkillAtlas</span>
                <span class="shrink-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActP4When">Hace 8 d</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-emerald-200/60 dark:border-emerald-900/40 bg-emerald-50/40 dark:bg-emerald-950/20 p-3">
            <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="dashboard.recent.techTitle">Tecnologías recientes</p>
            <ul class="m-0 mt-2 list-none space-y-2 p-0 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 min-w-0" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActT1">SQL</span>
                <span class="shrink-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActT1When">Hace 2 d</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 min-w-0" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActT2">Supabase</span>
                <span class="shrink-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActT2When">Hace 4 d</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 min-w-0" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActT3">Astro</span>
                <span class="shrink-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActT3When">Hace 6 d</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 min-w-0" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActT4">Tailwind CSS</span>
                <span class="shrink-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewActT4When">Hace 9 d</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center pt-1">
      <a
        href="/app"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-violet-600 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-violet-700 no-underline"
        data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewCtaApp"
      >
        Ver mi dashboard
      </a>
      <a
        href="/login"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900 no-underline"
        data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewCtaLogin"
      >
        Entrar
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
